summary.span: 提供一个将所有跟踪和调试输出路由到 IIS 7.0 基础结构的侦听器。

span.span: Provides a listener that routes all tracing and debugging output to the IIS 7.0 infrastructure.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 类连接的跟踪机制[!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)]到[!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)]。The class connects the tracing mechanism of [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] to [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)]. 此侦听器类使开发人员创建[!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)]应用程序和人员实现和页级、 模块级或处理程序级别对引发事件的接口[!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)]时跟踪基础结构已启用。This listener class enables developers who create [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] applications and who implement the and interfaces to raise page-level, module-level, or handler-level events to the [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] infrastructure when tracing is enabled. > [!NOTE] > 此侦听器类不路由[!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)]ASP.NET 类的事件。This listener class does not route [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] events to ASP.NET classes. 这包括类和实现的类或接口。This includes the class and classes that implement the or interface. 中引入[!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)]。 is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)]. 有关详细信息，请参见[版本和依赖关系](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md)。For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
